text: Langenargen is a municipality in Bodensee in Baden-Württemberg in Germany. == Twin towns == Langenargen is twinned with: * Arbon, Switzerland (1963) * Höckendorf, Germany (1990) * Bois-le-Roi, Seine-et-Marne, France (1991) * Noli, Italy (2005) == References == Category:Bodenseekreis
title: Langenargen
